markets.title: Will a bill that limits, restricts, or bans--or which gives the Executive Branch the power to limit, restrict, or ban--students from the People's Republic of China from attending universities and colleges in the United States becomes law before Dec 31, 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If a bill that limits, restricts, or bans--or which gives the Executive Branch the power to limit, restrict, or ban--students from the People's Republic of China from attending universities and colleges in the United States becomes law before Dec 31, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
